  },
  {
    q: "Where in LA do Wolf outdoor built-in pizza ovens concentrate?",
    a: "LA's luxury outdoor kitchen build geography concentrates Wolf ICBOGP installs in specific zip-code areas: <b>Bel Air</b> + <b>Beverly Hills</b> flats + <b>Holmby Hills</b> + <b>Pacific Palisades</b> + <b>Malibu</b> (both PCH oceanfront and Point Dume inland) + <b>Calabasas</b> (luxury hillside) + <b>Hidden Hills</b> + <b>Brentwood</b> estate tier + <b>Santa Monica</b> north-of-Montana luxury. These are the LA high-net-worth zip codes where $50k+ outdoor kitchen builds commonly include Sub-Zero Group matched-suite integration — and where Wolf ICBOGP is the specification rather than a portable Ooni or Gozney on a countertop. Secondary cluster: Newport Beach + Laguna Beach + Corona del Mar coastal OC luxury + Montecito + Santa Barbara inland luxury (Ventura County service overlap)."
